    <b>Who cares about Halloween? We've got PoP!</b></font><br>
    <font size=1><b>Date:</b> Tuesday, November 05 @ 09:12:11 CET<br><b>Topic:</b> News</font><br><br>
    </center>
    <font size="2">
    <b><h1><center>SILVERX AM PIGS!</center></h1></b><br><br>

Hooray! Planes of Power is out, atleast to most of us. It's been a busy week, lots of exping has been done, lots of new areas have been explored. It's been great fun really! I've got to say, this is by far the best expansion to date so far. Sure it has some bugs, some things that could be different and all that, but really, I'm going to have to say kudos to the brainsurgeons at Verant.<br><br>

I have got to say, I am very impressed with how they handeled flags. The character flag idea is simply great, and I love how NPC's react differently after you have solved a quest. But hey, anyway, here's some new encounters we've found.<br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerindar.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aramin.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/banord.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/falto.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/grummus.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/gryme.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/hohevent.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/jeplak.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/treefrog.JPG><br><br>We've also been busy in Halls of Honor, doing the trials there, but havnt really gotten any screenshots apart from the crazed norrathians. We've been farming Aerin´Dar like crazy lately...And while I'll be the first to say that these loots doesnt do him justice. They're not really 'bad', but frankly, the small tree frog should be dropping them, and he should have some better stuff. Here's what we've gotten from him.<br><br><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinloot.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinloot2.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinloot3.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinamulet.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinstaff.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinring.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinsword.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/aerinwrath.JPG></center><br><br>None of the other crap here have dropped anything even remotely good, actually, you could go to bazaar and buy better stuff than every single last one of the loots we've gotten from the other mobs. Really, the best comparison to this i can think of is when you phone the stupid pizzaria, the nice guy picks up and says "Esperia Pizza, hello" in his rough voice, after which you spend 5 minutes trying to tell him that you want really really much goddam pepperoni on it, in fact, you're paying for quadruple pepperoni just to make sure he understands that you dont want to be able to see the stuff underneath it, then you go pick it up and what do you see? A lowly shitty measly dumb amount of pepperoni. God I hate that.<br><br>I've gotta say it's really really beautiful, as far as uber fights go. They said they wanted to eliminate the CH chain, and while they havnt completely done it, they've done a very good job of getting near it though. Fights in PoP definitely are fast and furious, and very very interesting. No more picking nose and watching TV while pressing a single button every few seconds for 30 minutes, atleast not what we've seen so far. Three words; Arsenio fucking Hall. If it doesnt make sense to you, ask Vipsindsyg. He'd be more than happy to explain. I think I'm gonna go ask him myself. Well, I'm not going to say much more here... There's lots to be done, lots to be explored and we're having the time of our lives. But what did we do until one week ago when only a handfull of us had PoP? We farmed the shit out of VT and Emperor ofcourse. Here's the new Aten loot:<br><br><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/atenloot.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/atenloot2.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/atenloot3.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/atenbracer.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/atenmail.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/atensleeves.JPG></center><br><br>...and here's the new Emperor loot...<br><br><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/emploot.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/emploot2.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/emploot3.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/emploot4.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/empcloak.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/empsword.JPG></center><br><br>Another one of the highlights of this expansion, if the ability to give others illusion, and our enchanters have been living that up to the fullest. Here's some pictures of the ugliest guildies around to date.<br><br><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/eueinuillusion.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/hratliillusion.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/jmichillusion.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/khaunsharillusion.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/rinderwahnillusion.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/vipsindsygillusion.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/zahliaillusion.JPG><br><br>I don't care what you or anyone else thinks or says, no illusion will ever beat Hratli as an ogre. That's top of the line, the best ever.</center><br><br><b>Quotes of the day:</b><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/ailly.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/cutepai.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/flippett.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/geka.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/ghazaki.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/hratli.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/hratli2.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/hratli3.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/hratli4.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/pop/jmich.GIF><br><br><img src=http://w